text: Saad AlـKhanfour Al-Rasheedi is a member of the Kuwaiti National Assembly, representing the fourth district. Born in 1965, Al-Rasheedi worked at the Interior Ministry before being elected to the National Assembly in 2008. Al- Rasheedi is an Independent deputy and is a member of the Al-Rashaydah tribe.Arab Times MP Profile ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Kuwaiti people of Arab descent Category:Members of the National Assembly of Kuwait
